comments: Gafford (WAS) turns slightly as he contests the driving shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs with Garland (CLE) during the follow-through.
Allen (CLE) turns toward Gafford (WAS) and marginal contact occurs with Gafford's front during the dunk attempt.
Beal (WAS) brings the ball across half-court within eight seconds.
Bertans (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Osman's (CLE) path and absorbs the contact.
Love (CLE) and Bertans (WAS) engage and disengage with one another as Bertans moves to set the pick.

Love (CLE) moves alongside Beal's (WAS) path to the basket and marginal contact occurs with Beal's lower half during the driving shot attempt. Allen (CLE) legally contests Beal's driving shot attempt.
Westbrook (WAS) and Garland (CLE) engage and disengage with one another as they move along the perimeter.
Bertans (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position as Garland (CLE) loses control of the ball prior to incidental body contact occurring.
Westbrook (WAS) and Garland (CLE) make incidental body contact with one another as they each attempt to retrieve the loose ball.

Replay review of the foul called on Mathews (WAS) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Mathews is late to the spot and does not establish a legal guarding position prior to the start of Allen's (CLE) upward motion.

Wade (CLE) has his hand extended forward when marginal contact occurs with Westbrook's (WAS) front along the sideline. Wade then goes to the floor in an attempt to steal the ball and marginal contact occurs with Westbrook's right leg.
Osman (CLE) commits a take foul on Westbrook (WAS).
Gafford (WAS) brushes Garland's (CLE) left arm after his gather and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Garland (CLE) initiates contact across Neto's (WAS) right arm as he attempts to tie Neto up. The contact occurs prior to any possible traveling violation.
Allen (CLE) and Gafford (WAS) make incidental body contact with one another as they each attempt to retrieve the rebound.
